Preliminary Investigation Committees to determine whether
or not there shall be an inquiry;
(z) the procedure for the inquiry by the Disciplinary Board;
(aa) the formation of a Fitness to Practise Committee for
complaints or information pertaining to registered medical
practitioners who are professionally incompetent or are
impaired by physical or mental disability;
(bb) the formation of an Evaluation Committee for the purpose of
evaluation and registration of medical practitioners;
(cc) the formation of an Ethics Committee to advise the Council
on issues related to ethics;
(dd) any other committee for the purposes of this Act; and
(ee) any other matter for carrying into the effect the objects and
purposes of this Act.
